``` {.python .cell-code}
Map = geemap.Map()
agra = ee.FeatureCollection('FAO/GAUL/2015/level2')\
        .filter(ee.Filter.eq('ADM2_NAME', 'Agra')).geometry()
dw_16 = ee.ImageCollection('GOOGLE/DYNAMICWORLD/V1')\
.filter(ee.Filter.date('2016-05-27', '2016-12-31'))\
.filterBounds(agra)\
.select('label')\
.mode()\
.eq(6)\
.clip(agra)
    
dw_20 = ee.ImageCollection('GOOGLE/DYNAMICWORLD/V1')\
.filter(ee.Filter.date('2020-05-27', '2020-12-31'))\
.filterBounds(agra)\
.select('label')\
.mode()\
.eq(6)\
.clip(agra)
```
:::

left_layer = geemap.ee_tile_layer(dw_16, {}, 'Agra 2016')
right_layer = geemap.ee_tile_layer(dw_20, {}, 'Agra 2020')
Map.split_map(left_layer, right_layer)
Map
